OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772539376
OL,3,CUS continues strikes on Iran as
OL,4,Cconflict spreads to Lebanon and Gulf
OL,5,Cstates
OL,7,FIn Iraq, a pro-Iranian militia claimed
OL,8,Fresponsibility for a drone attack
OL,9,Ftargeting US troops at the Baghdad
OL,10,Fairport, the day after it said it
OL,11,Ffired at a US base in the city of
OL,12,FIrbil in the north, and Cyprus said a
OL,13,Fdrone attack targeted a British base
OL,14,Fon the Mediterranean island nation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772539376
OL,3,CUS continues strikes on Iran as
OL,4,Cconflict spreads to Lebanon and Gulf
OL,5,Cstates
OL,7,FIsrael and the US bombed Iranian
OL,8,Fmissile sites and targeted its navy,
OL,9,Fclaiming to have destroyed its
OL,10,Fheadquarters and multiple warships.
OL,11,FMore than 200 people have been killed
OL,12,Fsince the start of the strikes,
OL,13,Faccording to Iranian leaders.
OL,15,FIn Kuwait, Americans have been urged
OL,16,Fto stay indoors and away from the US
OL,17,Fembassy after it was struck by a drone
OL,18,Fovernight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772539376
OL,3,CUS continues strikes on Iran as
OL,4,Cconflict spreads to Lebanon and Gulf
OL,5,Cstates
OL,7,FHezbollah has also said it has entered
OL,8,Fthe war, firing missiles from Lebanon
OL,9,Fon early Monday into Israel; there was
OL,10,Fno report of casualties.
OL,12,FIsrael retaliated with strikes killing
OL,13,F31 people in South Lebanon and Beirut.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
