PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772539376
OL,3,CUS continues strikes on Iran as
OL,4,Cconflict spreads to Lebanon and Gulf
OL,5,Cstates
OL,7,FIran continues to be hit by the full
OL,8,Fforce of the US military, with B-2
OL,9,Fstealth bombers used to strike Iran's
OL,10,Fballistic missile facilities with
OL,11,F2,000-pound bombs, and President
OL,12,FDonald Trump claiming that nine
OL,13,FIranian warships had been sunk and
OL,14,Ftheir naval base largely destroyed.
OL,16,FIn Cyprus, a drone hit RAF Akrotiri,
OL,17,Fbut no casualties were reported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772539376
OL,3,CUS continues strikes on Iran as
OL,4,Cconflict spreads to Lebanon and Gulf
OL,5,Cstates
OL,7,FOfficials say the damage was limited,
OL,8,Fbut some people on the military bases
OL,9,Fin the region would undergo a
OL,10,F"temporary dispersal" as a safety
OL,11,Fmeasure.
OL,13,FOver the weekend, Keir Starmer gave
OL,14,Fthe US permission to use UK bases to
OL,15,Fstrike at Iranian missile sites.
OL,17,FBritain has so far not been involved
OL,18,Fin the US-Israeli strikes on Iran, and
OL,19,Fis reported to have previously refused
OL,20,FAmerican requests to use UK bases for
OL,21,Foperations against the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772539376
OL,3,CUS continues strikes on Iran as
OL,4,Cconflict spreads to Lebanon and Gulf
OL,5,Cstates
OL,7,FTalks between the US and Iran aimed at
OL,8,Fresolving the issue of Tehran's
OL,9,Fnuclear ambitions ended on Thursday
OL,10,Fwithout agreement, but were expected
OL,11,Fto resume at a later date.
OL,13,FBut instead, on Saturday, the US and
OL,14,FIsrael launched a "pre-emptive" strike
OL,15,Fagainst a Tehran government intent on
OL,16,Fdeveloping nuclear weapons.
OL,26,@vD@SOUvD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
