FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772539376
OL,3,CUS continues strikes on Iran as
OL,4,Cconflict spreads to Lebanon and Gulf
OL,5,Cstates
OL,7,FIran's Supreme Leader, Ayatollah Ali
OL,8,FKhamenei, was a long-time target of
OL,9,Fthe US and Israel, and was killed
OL,10,Fduring the coordinated daytime strikes
OL,11,Fon Tehran on Saturday morning.
OL,13,FIran has vowed to retaliate with
OL,14,F"devastating blows" and has fired
OL,15,Fmissiles at many of its neighbouring
OL,16,Fcountries as well as US military
OL,17,Ftargets.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
