OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772539376
OL,3,CUS continues strikes on Iran as
OL,4,Cconflict spreads to Lebanon and Gulf
OL,5,Cstates
OL,7,FThe strikes continued on Sunday with
OL,8,FIsrael saying it was taking its
OL,9,Fattacks to the "heart" of the Iranian
OL,10,Fcapital.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FIran retaliated by firing missiles and
OL,18,Fdrones at Israel and at US military
OL,19,Finstallations around the Gulf, and
OL,20,Falso at the Saudi capital and the
OL,21,Fglobal business hub of Dubai.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772539376
OL,3,CUS continues strikes on Iran as
OL,4,Cconflict spreads to Lebanon and Gulf
OL,5,Cstates
OL,7,FIsraeli authorities reported Iranian
OL,8,Fmissiles had killed nine civilians in
OL,9,FBeit Shemesh, near Jerusalem, while
OL,10,Fthe US military's Central Command said
OL,11,Fthree American service members had
OL,12,Fbeen killed and five others severely
OL,13,Fwounded on Sunday.
OL,15,FBritish nationals are among the
OL,16,Fhundreds of thousands of travellers
OL,17,Fstranded in Gulf Arab states, as major
OL,18,Fairports, including Dubai, remained
OL,19,Fclosed following retaliatory strikes
OL,20,Ffrom Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
