FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772539376
OL,3,CUS continues strikes on Iran as
OL,4,Cconflict spreads to Lebanon and Gulf
OL,5,Cstates
OL,7,FOfficials at the UK Foreign Office are
OL,8,Funderstood to be working on plans for
OL,9,Fpotential evacuation routes should
OL,10,Fairspace in the Gulf remain closed.
OL,12,FAround 94,000 people have already
OL,13,Fregistered their presence with the
OL,14,FForeign Office online, a scheme the
OL,15,FGovernment has used before to provide
OL,16,Furgent updates to people affected by
OL,17,Finternational crises.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
